@startuml
title UC14 - Frontend Classes
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
class NotificationBell { unreadCount +toggle(): void }
class NotificationDropdown { +loadMore(): void }
class NotificationItem { type title body isRead matchId +onClick(): void }
class NotificationApiClient {
  +list(): Promise<Notification[]>
  +unreadCount(): Promise<number>
  +markRead(id): Promise<void>
}
NotificationBell --> NotificationDropdown
NotificationDropdown --> NotificationItem
NotificationBell --> NotificationApiClient
NotificationDropdown --> NotificationApiClient
note bottom of NotificationItem
  WON hiển thị gold nhận được; click -> điều hướng tới match.
end note
@enduml
